{"tid":631511,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求人生道師教我點選擇","createTime":"2018-04-16T13:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T22:39:29.000Z","uid":44840,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7442d88fab0a918f955ef7c80a7043db4009e08e","tid":631511,"uid":44840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T13:51:26.000Z","msg":"背景：23歲/中六畢業<br />\n20歲開始入行 人工$16000<br />\n第一間做左1年就走左<br />\n但係就係果到識到依家個老闆（果陣仲係同事）<br />\n<br />\n咁我第一份工冇做之後<br />\n佢過一排都冇做（原來佢自己開一間黎做）<br />\n之後佢又叫我去幫佢手 咁我又冇工返緊 就去啦<br />\n<br />\n一開始都好地地<br />\n佢俾我人工都係$16000<br />\n做左3個月 開始穩定 佢就加我人工<br />\n去到17000 另加花紅（+2000/+4000 達到個額就有）<br />\n<br />\n就咁維持左兩年 花紅個個月都有（因為每個月都到額）係兩年間冇加過人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就今年3月 成班同事做到爆數 （例如由目標40去到68）多左50%以上出黎 <br />\n老闆就係出糧果陣話因爲商場要加租<br />\n要將個花紅目標提高先有花紅分<br />\n<br />\n咁我就諗 2年黎冇加過人工都算<br />\n仲要提高個花紅額 姐係簡單d講變相減人工<br />\n個心緊係唔舒服啦 做到爆數都要減人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以過左一星期左右我就話唔做啦<br />\n咁佢都有問我原因<br />\n我答想轉下環境/可能會轉行<br />\n<br />\n隔一日佢又捉我傾計<br />\n話加我人工 直接+5000俾我 要我留低幫佢手<br />\n<br />\n選擇1:留低 人工高27000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇野學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇老闆口面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n選擇2:第二間 人工得20000-22000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有野學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e012ef83cb2739e8e5931d422de67a7665ff56","tid":631511,"uid":44840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:03:16.000Z","msg":"我老母就話人工要緊 做多幾年就自己開一間<br />\n<br />\n但係我就話 出去學多d野仲好 但係個人工又好撚吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a330a4a1024028231e887eca859998f80b01e0","tid":631511,"uid":88785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"叫佢升你title 再留低半年至一年 跟住跳 <br />\n你要既係糧單同CV<br />\n<br />\nTitle都唔肯比你 就寧願去做20k學野算"},{"pid":"9e4a6f0cbd7859ec9aea03b97fe5303060a89058","tid":631511,"uid":44840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83a330a4a1024028231e887eca859998f80b01e0","tid":631511,"uid":88785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"叫佢升你title 再留低半年至一年 跟住跳 <br />\n你要既係糧單同CV<br />\n<br />\nTitle都唔肯比你 就寧願去做20k學野算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:23:20.000Z","msg":"已經係最高 <br />\n成間鋪都係我話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2286dfecfdb8b2465d082ce7c3ecbfdad72e3bde","tid":631511,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:31:52.000Z","msg":"咩行業先"},{"pid":"78a642bc73300f213e05e1f48b04fb1a895b06c2","tid":631511,"uid":68736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"呢D老闆正仆街黎 係我一定走 最憎人無口齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c3f7071fc33ddece5c7bcd538020d6d3a60b4f","tid":631511,"uid":167757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:43:11.000Z","msg":"梗係要錢啦，最好就係度留埋下半世做到退休"},{"pid":"0f5de665ce2e490f4f528c25b7c651fa92e6f3c2","tid":631511,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"23歲u grad𢭃緊13k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d268bde5698714c09eefd8c59127208063ff682e","tid":631511,"uid":88785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e4a6f0cbd7859ec9aea03b97fe5303060a89058","tid":631511,"uid":44840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83a330a4a1024028231e887eca859998f80b01e0","tid":631511,"uid":88785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"叫佢升你title 再留低半年至一年 跟住跳 <br />\n你要既係糧單同CV<br />\n<br />\nTitle都唔肯比你 就寧願去做20k學野算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:23:20.000Z","msg":"已經係最高 <br />\n成間鋪都係我話事<img src=\"